item.title: CVE-2017-20124|2024-08-05T21:45:26.154Z -- unspecified -- online%20hotel%20booking%20system%20pro%20plugin
item.description: A vulnerability classified as critical has been found in Online Hotel Booking System Pro Plugin 1.0. Affected is an unknown function of the file /front/roomtype-details.php. The manipulation of the argument tid leads to sql injection. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
